    <stitle>STEERABLE DRIVE AXLE END UNIT: FABCO - LUBRICATION - KINGPIN BEARINGS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="lubricate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>KINGPIN BEARINGS</title>
        <para>To ensure thorough lubrication of the kingpin bearings, block the rear wheels, raise and safely support
            the front axle to relieve weight. The lower kingpin lube fitting is located in the bottom of the lower
            kingpin ball stud itself. The upper kingpin fitting is on the steering arm or upper kingpin cap.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
